CustomField.description: The number of seconds spent talking on outbound calls which have been made by the User regardless of whether those calls connected or not. Note that calls to internal extensions that don't connect are also regarded as outbound calls. This statistic only records where the originator has not transferred the call, i.e. the originator actually dialled the initial call.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: "How many seconds of talk time have I spent on outbound calls from my organisation where the call was not transferred"
CustomField.label: Outbound Talk Seconds as Primary
